# **RELATIONSHIPS (UML Notation)**

```
VirtualMonitoringCenter "1" *-- "many" VirtualSoftwareAgent
VirtualMonitoringCenter "1" *-- "many" MonitoringUnit
VirtualMonitoringCenter "1" *-- "1" OrganizationalHierarchy

VirtualSoftwareAgent "1" --> "1" MonitoringUnit
VirtualSoftwareAgent "1" --> "1" VirtualWorkstation
VirtualSoftwareAgent "1" --> "1" KnowledgeBase
VirtualSoftwareAgent "1" --> "1" DecisionActionEngine

DecisionActionEngine "1" --> "1" ReportingAndEscalation
ReportingAndEscalation "1" --> "1" SupervisoryAgent

SupervisoryAgent "1" --> "1" LessonsLearnedRepository
LessonsLearnedRepository "1" --> "*" VirtualSoftwareAgent (rule updates)
LessonsLearnedRepository "1" --> "*" MonitoringUnit (threshold updates)
```

